<title>USA: Beachport, JB Oxford settle suit.</title>
<headline>Beachport, JB Oxford settle suit.</headline>
<dateline>LOS ANGELES 1997-07-09</dateline>
<text>
<p>Beachport Entertainment Corp Wednesday said it settled a lawsuit involving JB Oxford Holdings Inc in which Beachport will receive $1.5 million in cash and 50,000 shares of Oxford common stock.</p>
<p>In a statement, Beachport said Oxford also agreed to buy 486,486 Beachport common shares from Beachport at $2.3125 a share. Further details were undisclosed.</p>
<p>Beachport develops, produces and distributes a diversified array of live family entertainment, sporting events and television programming.</p>
